OL,3,CPedestrians injured by ladder falling
OL,4,Cfrom passing truck
OL,6,FTwo pedestrians have been injured
OL,7,Fafter a ladder fell off a passing
OL,8,Ftruck and hit them.
OL,10,FThe incident happened between 12:45pm
OL,11,Fand 1:05pm on Tuesday (21 July) along
OL,12,FLa Grande Route de la Cote in the
OL,13,FJersey parish of St Clement.
OL,15,FThe vehicle was carrying scaffolding
OL,16,Fpoles and heading down the road
OL,17,Ftowards the Rice Bowl Chinese
OL,18,Frestaurant.
OL,26,@tD@Xsw
