OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784917110
OL,3,CPedestrians injured by ladder falling
OL,4,Cfrom passing truck
OL,6,FA woman and a child were walking on
OL,7,Fthe pavement closest to the beach,
OL,8,Fbetween the Hotel Ambassadeur and M&S
OL,9,FFood store, when a ladder came off the
OL,10,Ftruck and struck them.
OL,12,FThe States of Jersey Police says the
OL,13,Fdriver did stop to check on them and
OL,14,Fcollect the ladder.
OL,16,FThe two pedestrians were assessed at
OL,17,Fthe island's General Hospital but have
OL,18,Fsince been discharged and are said to
OL,19,Fhave non life-changing minor injuries.
