OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1784917110
OL,3,CPedestrians injured by ladder falling
OL,4,Cfrom passing truck
OL,6,FAn investigation into the incident is
OL,7,Fongoing and the force is asking anyone
OL,8,Fwho may have seen what happened or has
OL,9,Finformation to contact them.
OL,11,FReports can be made by calling 01534
OL,12,F612612, while details can also be
OL,13,Fshared anonymously through the charity
OL,14,FCrimestoppers by ringing 0800 555111.
OL,16,FThe truck is described as having a
OL,17,Fgrey and red cab with a red diagonal
OL,18,Fstripe through the centre.
