OL,3,CPedestrians injured by ladder falling
OL,4,Cfrom passing truck
OL,6,FThe child was dressed in a matching
OL,7,Fcream t-shirt and shorts, while the
OL,8,Fwoman wore a black dress and had blue
OL,9,Fshoes.
